json-fortran
------------------------------------------
A user-friendly, thread-safe, and object-oriented API for reading and writing
JSON files, written in modern Fortran.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.1.7-1
  libgcc1-10.2.0-1
  libgfortran5-10.2.0-1
  libjsonfortran-devel-8.2.1-1bl1
  libjsonfortran8.2-8.2.1-1bl1
  pkg-config-1.6.3-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.34+1git.de9c1b7cfe-1
  cmake-3.17.3-2
  cygport-0.34.0-1
  gcc-core-10.2.0-1
  gcc-fortran-10.2.0-1
  gcc-g++-10.2.0-1
  make-4.3-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/jacobwilliams/json-fortran

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/jacobwilliams/json-fortran/archive/8.2.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack json-fortran-8.2.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./json-fortran-8.2.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/json-fortran-8.2.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/json-fortran-8.2.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libjsonfortran8.2-8.2.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libjsonfortran-devel-8.2.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(json-fortran)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/json-fortran.README
  /usr/share/doc/json-fortran/CHANGELOG.md
  /usr/share/doc/json-fortran/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/json-fortran/README.md
  /usr/share/doc/json-fortran/json-fortran-32x32.png
  /usr/share/doc/json-fortran/json-fortran-logo.svg
  /usr/share/doc/json-fortran/json-fortran.md

(libjsonfortran8.2)
  /usr/bin/cygjsonfortran-8.2.dll

(libjsonfortran-devel)
  /usr/include/json_get_scalar_by_path.inc
  /usr/include/json_get_vec_by_path.inc
  /usr/include/json_get_vec_by_path_alloc.inc
  /usr/include/json_initialize_arguments.inc
  /usr/include/json_initialize_dummy_arguments.inc
  /usr/include/json_macros.inc
  /usr/lib/cmake/jsonfortran-gnu-8.2.1/jsonfortran-gnu-config-version.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/jsonfortran-gnu-8.2.1/jsonfortran-gnu-config.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/jsonfortran-gnu-8.2.1/jsonfortran-gnu-targets-release.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/jsonfortran-gnu-8.2.1/jsonfortran-gnu-targets.cmake
  /usr/lib/libjsonfortran.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/json-fortran.pc

